session.  
</p>
<p> 3  United Nations Development Fund for Women (UNIFEM), Pacific Regional Office and Ministry of 
Women, Youth, and Children's Affairs, <i>Protecting women's human rights in Solomon Islands law,</i> 
Suva, 2009, pp. 61-62. 
</p>
<p> 4  UNDP and Ministry of Development, Planning and Aid Coordination, Millennium Development 
Goals Progress Report for Solomon Islands 2010 (available from 
www.undp.org.fj/pdf/Final_SI_MDG.pdf), p. 70. 
</p>
<p> 5  UNIFEM, Protecting Women&#8217;s Human Rights (see footnote 3), p. 65. 
